The '''Sienar Systems augmentor''' was a device, probably placed in a jet exhaust port, to provide extra thrust. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] tried to get one on the [[Black market/Legends|black market]] for the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']], but only obtained one after the ''Falcon'' was completely refitted before the [[Black Fleet Crisis]].

